fields.value: Nursing and its importance in future

dsDescriptionValue.value: Nursing can be characterized as an art and as well as science a heart and mind. At its heart lies a basic respect for human dignity and patient’s needs. It is supported by mind, in a practice of precise and rigorous core learning. And because of the vast range of specialization and complex nature of skills in the nursing profession, each nurse has specific strengths, passions and expertise. However, in a field as varied as nursing, there is no standard answer.
